{"tid":1246674,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人加油 - 假使世界原來不像你預期 (Offical MV) It's still Hong Kong","createTime":"2019-06-20T23:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T11:50:04.000Z","uid":266279,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9f51a1167170d9e182772087dd99419e97ca73da","tid":1246674,"uid":266279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T23:15:25.000Z","msg":"感謝每個走出來的香港人, 送給你們, 加油!  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ao1z5o-Fr2A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dao1z5o-Fr2A&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=291b583f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ao1z5o-Fr2A</a><br />\n<br />\n本片紀錄 2019年香港政府對《逃犯條例》修訂，香港人盡一切努力反映訴求，表達對此修訂的不滿<br />\n<br />\n感謝本片中出現的香港人:<br />\n黃耀明 陳日君樞機 陳順意 何潔明 朱凱迪 郭榮鏗 鄺俊宇 周庭 何韻詩 岑子杰 民陣各成員<br />\n<br />\nBoss: 建制派議員, 石禮謙, 防暴警察, 速龍小隊, 李家超, 林鄭月娥 <br />\n<br />\n假使世界原來不像你預期：<br />\n作曲/作詞/主唱：方皓玟<br />\n編曲：孔奕佳 許創基<br />\n監製：許創基<br />\n<br />\n影片來源: 民間人權陣線(民陣), 立法會新聞, VICE News, HBO, RFA 自由亞洲粵語, TVB新聞台, Bloomberg, Vision Times, TMHK, 東京TBS, CNN, BBC News, 大紀元, Billy Lai, 讀者謝先生 <br />\n<br />\n影片剪接及製作: 一個小小的香港市民 Jason (JTV)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感謝所有為不公義發聲的香港人 多謝你們為香港創下奇蹟...<br />\nIt's still Hong Kong, not China... not yet, not yet..."},{"pid":"859b156d8e47881a83608d09f529c05c150a8c88","tid":1246674,"uid":266279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:05:33.000Z","msg":"總部既朋友頂住呀"},{"pid":"cbb91e3784aaf33da6792bf39af7e0fce6a3fdf9","tid":1246674,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:12:38.000Z","msg":"香港人加油💪🏻"},{"pid":"f1e6d0d007abc3581e90348cd01cb6eb3ffa5bc9","tid":1246674,"uid":266279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T00:33:18.000Z","msg":"推推 希望喜歡的朋友可以Share呢條片出去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27f84137bd74b569cd774d0138750f070066b53","ti